    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1233.3333333,
          "startTime": 1.2333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "おはよう。悪いわね、急に付き合わせて",
      "startTime": 2.3666665475,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "今日は理想の花嫁のイメージを作り込むって\n聞いてますけど……俺は一体何をすれば？",
      "startTime": 9.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "私がこれから、私なりに考えた理想の花嫁キャラを\n演じてみせるから、意見を言ってほしいの",
      "startTime": 17.7742767781,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "こういうのって、独りよがりになるとダメじゃない？\n第三者からどう見えるかが大事でしょ",
      "startTime": 24.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "特に男性からの意見がほしいの\n結婚って、花婿と花嫁のどちらが欠けても出来ないから",
      "startTime": 30.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "俺が莉央さんの花婿役をやるってことですか？",
      "startTime": 35.2333332141,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "ち、違うわよ！　変なこと言わないでちょうだい！",
      "startTime": 38.7333319426,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "一応言っておくけど、このことは絶対秘密よ！？\n特にLizNoirのメンバーには！",
      "startTime": 46.8333320618,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "CMで、私の完璧な花嫁っぷりをいきなり見せつけて\n敗北を味わわせるんだから……！！",
      "startTime": 53.3389379159,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "花嫁に勝ちも負けもないと思いますけど……",
      "startTime": 55.5333332141,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "私にはあるのよ！　いくわよ、まずは表情よ！\n可愛らしい花嫁のスマイルを作り込むわ！",
      "startTime": 63.9333307902,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "ど、どうかしら？　正直に感想を言ってちょうだい",
      "startTime": 66.933330671,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "えっと……笑顔というより\n何かを企んでるような表情に見えます",
      "startTime": 74.4333307902,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "なんですって！？　失礼ね！！",
      "startTime": 77.5333362658,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そもそも無理に可愛く笑う必要はないんですよ\n普段のクールでかっこいい姿が求められていますから",
      "startTime": 83.333336385,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "……む。そうね。確かにその通りだわ\nでも、いつもの私のままって訳にはいかないわ",
      "startTime": 91.2000030517,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "私にだって、理想の花嫁のイメージがあるのよ\nそれを、この仕事で表現してみたいの",
      "startTime": 99.6000086466,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "その気持ちを抑え込んでしまったら……\nそれこそ、神崎莉央らしくないわ",
      "startTime": 106.0000086466,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "なら、自分らしさを見失わないように気を付けつつ\n莉央さんなりの花嫁像を表現していきましょうか",
      "startTime": 113.1000086466,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、分かったわ。もう大丈夫\n作りものっぽくならないように注意するわね",
      "startTime": 120.5396376661,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（良かった。これなら大丈夫そうだ）",
      "startTime": 123.4333418607,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02-rio015.m4a",
      "text": "……ちょっと、何をにやにやしてるのよ\nこっちを見ないでちょうだい",
      "startTime": 129.9269406422,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "み、見るなって言われても\nそれじゃあ表情のチェックが出来ませんよ……",
      "startTime": 135.1333480834,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02-rio016.m4a",
      "text": "今日の練習はこれで終わりね\n……そういえば、撮影当日は誰が立ち会うの？",
      "startTime": 143.7666814167,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "橋本さんに頼んでいますけど、それが何か？",
      "startTime": 147.4000278551,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02-rio017.m4a",
      "text": "な、なんでもないわ\nそれで、今日は帰っていいのかしら？",
      "startTime": 153.5666814167,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "もう少しだけ時間を下さい。クライアントが\n莉央さんの結婚観についてアンケートを取りたいそうで",
      "startTime": 159.0468566119,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02-rio018.m4a",
      "text": "アンケート？　……まぁいいわ。さっさと始めましょう",
      "startTime": 162.5333611885,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます。では最初のアンケートです\n結婚相手に求めることは？",
      "startTime": 171.4333480834,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02-rio019.m4a",
      "text": "そうね、親密なコミュニケーションかしら\n好きな人といるんだから、いろんなことを話したいわ",
      "startTime": 177.6333480834,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02-rio020.m4a",
      "text": "仕事のこと、趣味のこと……お互いに刺激し合って\n高め合える関係が理想的ね",
      "startTime": 185.7333480834,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "いいですね。では次のアンケートです\n家事の分担はどういう形が望ましいですか？",
      "startTime": 192.3666814167,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02-rio021.m4a",
      "text": "平等に分担するのが理想なんでしょうけど……\n無理やり平等にしても、長続きしないと思うの",
      "startTime": 199.5666814167,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02-rio022.m4a",
      "text": "だから二人で話し合って決めたいわ\nあっ、でも、料理は好きだから任せてほしいかしら",
      "startTime": 205.6666814167,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02-rio023.m4a",
      "text": "たまには旦那さんの手料理も食べてみたいけれど\n……ふふっ、ちょっと求め過ぎてる？",
      "startTime": 213.2666814167,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "（いい感じだ。莉央さんの理想のイメージと）\n（莉央さんらしさが両方ともよく出てる）",
      "startTime": 219.9000147501,
      "sfxList": []
