      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_02-rio028.m4a",
      "text": "私のパートナーなら、私の仕事を理解して\n目一杯応援してくれるはずだもの",
      "startTime": 264.8333501178,
      "sfxList": []
